		&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;We are in this field for a quite number of years and have vast experience in real estate business. We have a many number of clients at our customer base in Coimbatore and also we cater to abroad customers. We are now concentrating mainly &lt;strong&gt;NEELAMBUR&lt;/strong&gt; and surrounding areas for our real estate business.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NEELMABUR : An area of lucrative investment opportunities.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;Neelambur and its surrounding areas of Coimbatore have the highest growth potential. Now the city is well connected through a network of highways. Therefore staying in Neelambur is no more considered to be an inconvenience. Infact, these are best locales with an abundance of open and green spaces. It comprises of good connectivity and transportation facilities, as well as amenities such as malls, schools, colleges, hospitals and residential houses.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;h5&gt;Location Advantages :&lt;/h5&gt;
		&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;Easy assess to prime life style, entertainment, shopping, healthcare and educational facilities.&lt;/p&gt;
